c: 46
v: 10
t: "Babaze (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Mutekereze nk’ubu iyi (Qur’an) ibaye ituruka kwa Allah mukaba muyihakana; nyamara umwe muri bene Isiraheli ahamya ko ari nka yo (ari ukuri nka Tawurati), akaba anayemera mu gihe mwe mwishyira hejuru (muyihakana)!” Mu by’ukuri Allah ntayobora abantu b’abahakanyi"